    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([b0].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t] ON [b].[BookId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b1].[Id], [b1].[CreationTime], [b1].[CreatorUserId], [b1].[DeleterUserId], [b1].[DeletionTime], [b1].[DepartmentId], [b1].[IsDeleted], [b1].[LastModificationTime], [b1].[LastModifierUserId], [b1].[Name]
    FROM [BookCategories] AS [b1]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([b1].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t0] ON [t].[BookCategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[CreationTime], [d].[CreatorUserId], [d].[DeleterUserId], [d].[DeletionTime], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[LastModificationTime], [d].[LastModifierUserId], [d].[Name]

) AS [t2] ON [b].[StudentId] = [t2].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (

    FROM [Department] AS [d0]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([d0].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t3] ON [t2].[StudentDepartmentId] = [t3].[Id]
WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([b].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))

WHERE (((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ((@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR [a].[TenantId] IS NULL)) AND ([a].[Id] = @__p_0)

FROM [Borrows] AS [b]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[BookAuthor], [b0].[BookCategoriesId], [b0].[BookPublisher], [b0].[BookTitle], [b0].[CreationTime], [b0].[CreatorUserId], [b0].[DeleterUserId], [b0].[DeletionTime], [b0].[IsBorrowed], [b0].[IsDeleted], [b0].[LastModificationTime], [b0].[LastModifierUserId]
    FROM [Book] AS [b0]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([b0].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t] ON [b].[BookId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b1].[Id], [b1].[CreationTime], [b1].[CreatorUserId], [b1].[DeleterUserId], [b1].[DeletionTime], [b1].[DepartmentId], [b1].[IsDeleted], [b1].[LastModificationTime], [b1].[LastModifierUserId], [b1].[Name]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[BookCategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]

    SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[CreationTime], [d].[CreatorUserId], [d].[DeleterUserId], [d].[DeletionTime], [d].[IsDeleted], [d].[LastModificationTime], [d].[LastModifierUserId], [d].[Name]

) AS [t2] ON [b].[StudentId] = [t2].[Id]

    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([d0].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t3] ON [t2].[StudentDepartmentId] = [t3].[Id]
WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([b].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))

) AS [t] ON [b].[BookId] = [t].[Id]

) AS [t2] ON [b].[StudentId] = [t2].[Id]

    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[CreationTime], [b0].[CreatorUserId], [b0].[DeleterUserId], [b0].[DeletionTime], [b0].[DepartmentId], [b0].[IsDeleted], [b0].[LastModificationTime], [b0].[LastModifierUserId], [b0].[Name]
